      "fieldId": "1a000001-0000-4000-a000-000000000001",
      "value": "Sub-field addressing"
    },
    {
      "fieldId": "1a000002-0000-4000-a000-000000000002",
      "value": "\nWeb UI comments and annotations attached to specific text within a Field value require addressing below the Field level. `ext:addressability` currently addresses at Field granularity. Sub-field text selection addressing is architecturally possible (the Address space accommodates it) but is deferred as a separate extension.\n\n---"
    }
  ],
